        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Small-Dollar PPP Forgiveness Simplification Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill makes changes to the Paycheck Protection Program (PPP) to with respect to forgiveness of certain PPP loans.</p> <p>Specifically, the bill includes as covered loans under the PPP loan forgiveness program excess loan amounts that were received due to a good faith error. </p> <p>The bill also increases the threshold, from $150,000 to $350,000, used to determine whether a PPP loan may use the simplified forgiveness application.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
